{"tw": {"2514850": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "女僕奴隸與黃金地城", "steam_appid": 2514850, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/ca4096431f1f3e5e5f4fc49be13584c8.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【女僕奴隸與黃金地城】一款由nikukyu製作，並由072 Project代理發行的短篇成人Roguelite遊戲。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/82ef9eeb4a8ba1a467f29fb2a78c6662.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不知為何，就這樣俘虜到了敵國出陣的將軍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿到了對方的奴隸權，還讓她做了女僕，但是好感度極差。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一個人過著這麼貧窮的生活，以後的生活該怎麼辦.....開始想念起充滿煩惱時的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當時冷漠的表情如今也變得溫和許多，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「是打算睡到甚麼時候，主人，今天也說好要下地城吧」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邊說著並用口交把我叫醒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在那場最糟的相遇幾年後， 今天也和好感度MAX的原將軍現役女僕奴隸一起下地城尋找可以賺錢的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/944358eb2215b911d1ddefc0b4a5a84b.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/5254425b2f13cb7f5890e2530edb47ad.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沒有麻煩的練等機制</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不需要重複打怪刷高等級，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇到怪物不想打還可以逃跑！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要透過強化武器，就可以提升數值，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同時獲得強力的技能！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite的地城設計</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨機生成的地圖機制，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是資源還是寶箱都是隨機生成，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次進入地城都有不一樣的體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特殊的飢餓與口渴值系統</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG少有的飢餓值與口渴值系統，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >進地城前都要檢查身上的食物和水是否足夠，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一不小心就有可能餓死在地城裡喔!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/0b7a0eb7b4a8fe46ee30f510a7aa4cf4.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回過神來你就和你的女僕過著性福快樂的生活，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是為了讓莉亞重獲自由之身，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >必須想辦法在這全部有60層的地城裡賺到100萬!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地城時你除了打怪和採集資源外，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還要當心你跟莉亞的飢餓與口渴值，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一個不注意可能就要回到第一層重新探索，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當湊齊裝備後就可以往更深的階層收集高價的資源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努力賺錢的途中說不定還會有各種「獎勵」等著你?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/85766d98dd886f3bf666fd814230a901.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/9a242a9783f586ce135e53316b558035.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/003d520d2cd2e927be8edcec7263f0cf.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳過劇情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全螢幕模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按鍵設置/搖桿設置</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隱藏對話框</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >場景回想</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG回想</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空腹值/飢渴值</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨機地城</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器強化</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/ca4096431f1f3e5e5f4fc49be13584c8.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【女僕奴隸與黃金地城】一款由nikukyu製作，並由072 Project代理發行的短篇成人Roguelite遊戲。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/82ef9eeb4a8ba1a467f29fb2a78c6662.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不知為何，就這樣俘虜到了敵國出陣的將軍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿到了對方的奴隸權，還讓她做了女僕，但是好感度極差。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一個人過著這麼貧窮的生活，以後的生活該怎麼辦.....開始想念起充滿煩惱時的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當時冷漠的表情如今也變得溫和許多，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「是打算睡到甚麼時候，主人，今天也說好要下地城吧」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邊說著並用口交把我叫醒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在那場最糟的相遇幾年後， 今天也和好感度MAX的原將軍現役女僕奴隸一起下地城尋找可以賺錢的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto