"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/85766d98dd886f3bf666fd814230a901.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/9a242a9783f586ce135e53316b558035.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/003d520d2cd2e927be8edcec7263f0cf.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳過劇情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全螢幕模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按鍵設置/搖桿設置</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隱藏對話框</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >場景回想</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG回想</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空腹值/飢渴值</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨機地城</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器強化</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "戰爭後，敵國女將軍「莉亞」竟成為了你的俘虜!? 為了讓身為奴隸女僕的莉亞重獲自由，必須在地城賺到一百萬才行，沒想到卻在地下城過起了甜蜜日子…?", "supported_languages": "日文, 英文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1762767277", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1762767277", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1762767277", "website": "https://072project.com/?source=steam_maidslaves&amp;utm_source=steam&amp;utm_medium=maidslaves&amp;utm_campaign=store_link", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2+ GHz Processor<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL ES 2.0 hardware driver support required for WebGL acceleration. (AMD Catalyst 10.9, nVidia 358.50)<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 MB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["nikukyu"], "publishers": ["072 Project", "072 News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 15800, "final": 15800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 158"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2023 年 9 月 15 日"}}}}, "us": {"2514850": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Maid Slaves & Golden Dungeon", "steam_appid": 2514850, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/ca4096431f1f3e5e5f4fc49be13584c8.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;Maid Slaves &amp; Golden Dungeon&quot; is a short adult Roguelite game developed by nikukyu and published by 072 Project.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/82ef9eeb4a8ba1a467f29fb2a78c6662.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By chance, the general who was captured became a prisoner of war in the enemy country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I also obtained the slave rights of her and made her a maid, but we have a bad relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I really miss the time when I lived in poverty and worried about my future life alone...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her cold expression back then has become much softer now,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While saying, &quot;&quot;Master, when do you wake up? You said you wanted to go to the dungeon today, right?&quot;&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And she woke me up with a &quot;blow&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A few years after that terrible encounter, today, I go to the dungeon to earn money with the former general who now is my maid!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/dd5b0f7447079b90f522c6219d707b8f.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/5254425b2f13cb7f5890e2530edb47ad.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No troublesome mechanics</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need to repeatedly fight monsters to level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even escape from monsters if you don't want to fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just enhance your weapons to increase your stats,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and gain powerful skills at the same time!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite dungeon design</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both resources and treasures are randomly generated,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >every time you enter the dungeon, you have a different experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique hunger and thirst system</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rare hunger and thirst system in RPGs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before entering the dungeon, you need to check if you have enough food and water,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Otherwise, you might starve to death in the dungeon!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/0b7a0eb7b4a8fe46ee30f510a7aa4cf4.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you come to your senses, you will live a happy and sex life with your maid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But in order to free Leia, you must find a way to earn 1 million in this 60 floors dungeon!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While exploring the dungeon, in addition to fighting monsters and gathering resources, you also need to be careful of your hunger and thirst with Ria.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One careless mistake and you might have to start exploring from the first level again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you gather the equipment, you can collect valuable resources in deeper levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you are working hard to earn money, there may be various &quot;rewards&quot; waiting for you?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/85766d98dd886f3bf666fd814230a901.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/83793ce3b4f2a6b7ab093a686d8b200c.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/0257807d5e241a36d08726a38b982c19.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skip the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fullscreen mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key settings / joystick settings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide dialogue box</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scene recollection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG recollection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunger value / Thirst value</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random dungeon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon enhancement</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/ca4096431f1f3e5e5f4fc49be13584c8.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;Maid Slaves &amp; Golden Dungeon&quot; is a short adult Roguelite game developed by nikukyu and published by 072 Project.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/82ef9eeb4a8ba1a467f29fb2a78c6662.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By chance, the general who was captured became a prisoner of war in the enemy country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I also obtained the slave rights of her and made her a maid, but we have a bad relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I really miss the time when I lived in poverty and worried about my future life alone...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her cold expression back then has become much softer now,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While saying, &quot;&quot;Master, when do you wake up? You said you wanted to go to the dungeon today, right?&quot;&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And she woke me up with a &quot;blow&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A few years after that terrible encounter, today, I go to the dungeon to earn money with the former general who now is my maid!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/dd5b0f7447079b90f522c6219d707b8f.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/5254425b2f13cb7f5890e2530edb47ad.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No troublesome mechanics</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need to repeatedly fight monsters to level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even escape from monsters if you don't want to fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just enhance your weapons to increase your stats,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and gain powerful skills at the same time!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite dungeon design</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both resources and treasures are randomly generated,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >every time you enter the dungeon, you have a different experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique hunger and thirst system</h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rare hunger and thirst system in RPGs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before entering the dungeon, you need to check if you have enough food and water,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Otherwise, you might starve to death in the dungeon!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514850/extras/0b7a0eb7b4a8fe46ee30f510a7aa4cf4.avif?t=1762767277\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you come to your senses, you will live a happy and sex life with your maid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But in order to free Leia, you must find a way to earn 1 million in this 60 floors dungeon!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While exploring the dungeon, in addition to fighting monsters and gathering resources, you also need to be careful of your hunger and thirst with Ria.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One careless mistake and you might have to start exploring from the first level again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you gather the equipment, you can collect valuable resources in deeper levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you are working hard to earn money, there may be